      %td
        #miracle
          %h1
            BE PART OF A MIRACLE!
          %p
            SMA - Spinal Muscular Atrophy - kills more babies than any other genetic disease. SMA is currently a death sentence. But, there is enormous HOPE! Research is on the brink of a cure, but in desperate need of funding.
          %p
            Our daughter, Gwendolyn, and thousands of other children are dying of SMA. We are fighting to end this disease and $1 Million will have an immediate and direct impact on making a cure attainable -- to save Gwendolyn, to save all children battling SMA, and to ensure no future babies are stolen by this cruel disease.
          %p
            $1 Million will help cure this disease forever and your simple, FREE vote through Facebook moves us one step closer to that miracle. Vote today and be part of it!
          
          %p
            %center
              = link_to "Click to vote for us on Facebook", 'http://apps.facebook.com/chasecommunitygiving/charities/710566'

